[+] Run directly
-------------------------------

  hardeningone can be executed directly (unpack tarball, enter hardeningone directory).

  # sh hardeningone
  or
  # ./hardeningone
  
  Make sure you have root privileges.
 


[+] Installation
-------------------------------

  If you want to install hardeningone, see the README file (section: Installation) for
  more tips about how to install or create a custom package.



[+] Documentation
-------------------------------

  Documentation about hardeningone can be found in the man page (man hardeningone, or
  hardeningone --man-page), README file and website. Also the FAQ file covers some
  often asked questions.



